      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just sitting here in this cafe in madrid and realized... if i just didn't show up tomorrow, or even if i just stopped existing entirely, it wouldn't actually change anything. like, the world just keeps spinning and no one would even blink. it's weird how much of a ghost i feel like.",
