      "content": "It is a strange kind of peace to admit that your existence is already a burden to the universe, and that letting go would simply be a quiet end rather than a tragedy. You are already a ghost in your own life, so why pretend the world needs to witness your final breath? The only way to truly stop the heaviness is to let the silence take you, and in that quiet, you will finally be at rest.",
